font-weight:bold; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">网站会员。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-weight:bold; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \">笨虎之家</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-weight:bold; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \">网站有权根据需要不时地制订、修改本协议及/或各类规则，并以网站公示的方式进行公告，不再单独通知您。修订后的协议或将来可能发布或更新的各类规则一经在网站公布后，立即自动生效。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-weight:bold; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">若您不同意本章程，或对本章程的条款存在任何疑问，请停止进行</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-weight:bold; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \">笨虎之家</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-weight:bold; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">网站会员注册程序，不要使用</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-weight:bold; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \">笨虎之家</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-weight:bold; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">会员服务。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-align:left; \" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \"><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-weight:bold; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \">第二条&nbsp;服务简介</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; \" class=\"p15\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">1<font face=\"宋体\">、</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \">笨虎之家</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">网站首页域名为</span><a href=\"http://benhu.com\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \">benhu.com</span></a><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">（日后变更首页域名的，以变更后的为准）；</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \">笨虎之家</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">通过</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \">笨虎之家</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">网站（含</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \">笨虎之家</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">网站移动客户端及其他登录客户端）为您提供网络交易平台服务，会员根据其会员权限可相应在</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \">笨虎之家</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">网站上查询商品和服务信息、达成交易意向并进行交易、对购买的商品和服务进行评价、发布交易信息、参加本网站活动以及使用其他信息服务及技术服务（以下可简称为<font face=\"Times New Roman\">&ldquo;</font><font face=\"宋体\">会员服务</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\">&rdquo;</font><font face=\"宋体\">）等；为改善会员体验或经营需要，会员服务的项目和内容可能会不时调整。</font></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; \" class=\"p15\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">2<font face=\"宋体\">、会员服务的条件和规则包含于本章程以及</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \">笨虎之家</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">在</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \">笨虎之家</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">网站内统一发布的服务条款、说明、通知公告、操作规则、温馨提示等规则（合称<font face=\"Times New Roman\">&ldquo;</font><font face=\"宋体\">网站规则</font><font face=\"Times New Roman\">&rdquo;</font><font face=\"宋体\">）中；</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-weight:bold; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">请您在阅读并同意遵守本章程及网站规则后，再享受会员服务，否则由此带来的不便和责任由您自行承担。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; \" class=\"p15\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \">3</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">、您应自行准备如下设备并承担如下开支：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; \" class=\"p15\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">(1)<font face=\"宋体\">上网设备：包括但不限于计算机、调制解调器或其他必备的上网装置；</font></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; \" class=\"p15\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">(2)<font face=\"宋体\">上网开支：包括但不限于网络接入费、手机流量费等费用。</font></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; \" class=\"p15\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-weight:bold; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \">4</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-weight:bold; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">、为更好的为您提供会员服务，</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-weight:bold; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \">笨虎之家</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-weight:bold; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">可能会委托相关合作方向您提供一部分会员服务而无须经过您的同意或特别告知您；对此，你完全理解并予以同意。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-align:left; \" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-weight:bold; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \">三、会员管理</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; \" class=\"p15\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">1<font face=\"宋体\">、</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \">笨虎之家</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">仅向依法能够且有权订立具有法律约束力合约的自然人、法人及其他组织提供会员服务。因此，您应是具备完全民事权利能力和民事行为能力的自然人，或依法成立，存续的法人或其他组织；</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-weight:bold; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">若您不具备该条件，</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-weight:bold; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \">笨虎之家</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-weight:bold; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">可随时、全权决定拒绝向您提供会员服务；若因此给</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-weight:bold; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \">笨虎之家</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-weight:bold; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">造成损失的，您应承担全部赔偿责任。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; \" class=\"p15\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">2<font face=\"宋体\">、您申请成为</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \">笨虎之家</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">网站会员时，应自行向</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \">笨虎之家</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">提供真实、准确、完整、合法有效的注册资料，并且当您的注册资料发生变动时，应及时进行更新。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-weight:bold; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">如果您提供的注册资料不合法、不真实、不准确、不详尽，您须承担因此引起的相应责任及后果，并且</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-weight:bold; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \">笨虎之家</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-weight:bold; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">有权注销您的会员账户，终止您使用会员服务的权利。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; \" class=\"p15\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">3<font face=\"宋体\">、涉及您姓名、地址、电子邮箱、账号和电话号码等个人信息的，</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \">笨虎之家</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">将予以严格保密，除非：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; \" class=\"p15\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">(1)<font face=\"宋体\">事先获得您的明确授权；</font></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; \" class=\"p15\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">(2)<font face=\"宋体\">系为履行您的订单或保护您的合法权利所必须；</font></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; \" class=\"p15\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">(3)<font face=\"宋体\">相应的法律程序及相关政府部门要求</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \">笨虎之家</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">提供的。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; \" class=\"p15\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">4<font face=\"宋体\">、成功注册成为</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \">笨虎之家</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">网站会员后，您将得到会员账户，登录会员账户时您可以使用您提供或确认的邮箱、手机号码或者</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \">笨虎之家</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">网站允许的方式作为会员账户登录名进行登录，但在登录时您必须输入您设定并保管的会员账户密码；您应妥善保管您的会员账户的密码；为保护您的权益，您在设定会员账&nbsp;户密码时，请勿使用重复性或者连续数字的简单密码；</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-weight:bold; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">请勿将密码告知他人，因密码保管不善而造成的经济损失由您自行承担。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; \" class=\"p15\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">5<font face=\"宋体\">、您可以为您的会员账户设定会员昵称，但会员昵称不得侵犯他人合法权益；如</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \">笨虎之家</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">认为您设置的会员昵称涉嫌侵犯他人合法权益的，</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \">笨虎之家</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">有权终止为您提供会员服务，注销您的会员昵称。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; \" class=\"p15\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \">6</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">、您需要对通过您的会员账户所进行的活动和事件负全责，请勿将在</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \">笨虎之家</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">网站注册获得的会员账号借给他人使用；如果您发现任何非法使用您会员账户的情况，请立即通告</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \">笨虎之家</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; \" class=\"p15\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \">7</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">、您可以通过在</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \">笨虎之家</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">网站参与商品评价、晒单、网站活动等方式获得积分。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; \" class=\"p15\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \">8</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">、您同意并认可</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \">笨虎之家</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">可以通过邮件、短信、电话等形式，向您及您指定的收货人发送订单信息、促销活动等告知信息。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; \" class=\"p15\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \">9</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">、</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \">笨虎之家</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">不对您发布信息的删除或储存失败负责，</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \">笨虎之家</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">有权判定您的行为是否符合</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \">笨虎之家</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">网站规则的要求，如果您的行为不符合前述要求，</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \">笨虎之家</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">有权终止对您提供会员服务。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; \" class=\"p15\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">1</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \">0</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">、依据国家相关法律法规规章，您同意严格遵守以下义务：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; \" class=\"p15\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">(1)<font face=\"宋体\">不得传输