nt-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \">笨虎之家</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">保留删除网站内涉嫌违反本</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \">服务协议</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">、法律法规政策及不真实的信息内容且无须通知您的权利。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; \" class=\"p15\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-weight:bold; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">若您未遵守以上规定的，</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-weight:bold; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \">笨虎之家</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-weight:bold; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">有权作出独立判断并采取暂停会员权限直至注销您的会员账户等措施，并且您须对自己的言论和行为承担法律责任。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; text-align:left; \" class=\"p0\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \"><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-weight:bold; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \">第四条&nbsp;商品信息</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:0pt; margin-top:0pt; \" class=\"p15\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-weight:bold; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">1<font face=\"宋体\">、</font></span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-weight:bold; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \">笨虎之家</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-weight:bold; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">网站上的商品信息随时有可能发生变动，</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-weight:bold; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \">笨虎之家</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-weight:bold; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'Times New Roman\'; \">对此不作特别通知。</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\'; font-weight:bold; font-size:12.0000pt; font-family:\'宋体\'; \">笨虎之家</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes