; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; margin: 0.83em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 1.5em; font-weight: 700; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255,0,0)\"><font face=\"楷体_GB2312\"><font color=\"#ff80c0\">产品材质：<span style=\"color: rgb(255,0,0)\">防尘盖（PP):采用食品级PP原料制成，可保持奶嘴干净卫生。</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255,0,0)\">耐温&mdash;20℃&mdash;110℃</span></font></font></span></h2>\r\n<h2 align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; margin: 0.83em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 1.5em; font-weight: 700; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255,0,0)\"><font face=\"楷体_GB2312\" color=\"#ff80c0\">螺牙盖（PP/TPE):弹性包胶及凸起设计与底座配合可有效保护玻璃身。耐温&mdash;20℃&mdash;110℃</font></span></h2>\r\n<h2 align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; margin: 0.83em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 1.5em; font-weight: 700; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255,0,0)\"><font face=\"楷体_GB2312\" color=\"#ff80c0\">奶嘴（silicone）：食品级液态活性硅胶精制而成，柔软富有弹性 不易撕裂。耐温~20℃~12℃</font></span></h2>\r\n<h2 align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; margin: 0.83em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 1.5em; font-weight: 700; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255,0,0)\"><font face=\"楷体_GB2312\" color=\"#ff80c0\">玻璃瓶身（硼硅玻璃）：采用高透明 耐热的硼硅玻璃制成 瓶身无接缝 容易清洗。耐温~20℃~160℃</font></span></h2>\r\n<h2 align=\"center\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; margin: 0.83em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 1.5em; font-weight: 700; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255,0,0)\"><font face=\"楷体_GB2312\" color=\"#ff80c0\">弹性底座（TPE):柔韧的底座及凸起设计防滑防滑动。耐温~20℃~110℃</font></span></h2>\r\n<h2 align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; margin: 0.83em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 1.5em; font-weight: 700; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255,0,0)\"><font face=\"楷体_GB2312\" color=\"#ff80c0\">产品特点：</font></span></h2>\r\n<h2 align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; margin: 0.83em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 1.5em; font-weight: 700; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255,0,0)\"><font face=\"楷体_GB2312\" color=\"#ff80c0\">1。日康丽宝玻璃奶瓶采用高透明 耐热的医用级硼硅玻璃制成 瓶身内表面光滑 不易积奶垢 容易清洗 具有良好的耐温度急变性能（例如倒入沸水）而不易爆裂 卫生安全</font></span></h2>\r\n<h2 align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; margin: 0.83em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 1.5em; font-weight: 700; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255,0,0)\"><font face=\"楷体_GB2312\" color=\"#ff80c0\">2.弹性包胶螺牙盖和底座 有效增强玻璃瓶体抗物理冲击能力 。包胶凸起设计可避免玻璃瓶身触碰硬质平面、地板，能有效的减少意外摔破几率，还能起到防滑跟放滚动效果，更有效的保护玻璃奶瓶。</font></span></h2>\r\n<h2 align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; margin: 0.83em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 1.5em; font-weight: 700; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255,0,0)\"><font face=\"楷体_GB2312\" color=\"#ff80c0\">3.奶嘴采用食品级液态活性硅胶精制而成，柔软富有弹性、不易撕裂。特种的变流量十字孔结构，可随宝宝吸吮力大小自动调节流量，使宝宝吸奶更加自如。</font></span></h2>\r\n<h2 align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; margin: 0.83em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 1.5em; font-weight: 700; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255,0,0)\"><font face=\"楷体_GB2312\" color=\"#ff80c0\">4.使用前请将各部件清洗干净，置于沸水中消毒3-5分钟，或采用日康微波消毒盒、奶瓶消毒器消毒。定期检查奶嘴，如有咬痕 破损 等现象应立即更换。奶瓶存放在清洁 干燥的容器内。</font></span></h2>\r\n<h2 align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; margin: 0.83em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 1.5em; font-weight: 700; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255,0,0)\"><font face=\"楷体_GB2312\" color=\"#ff80c0\">5。装有奶水的奶瓶可在微波炉内加热（不包括瓶身意外的部件）。</font></span></h2>\r\n<h2 align=\"left\" style=\"padding-bottom: 0px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; margin: 0.83em 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(0,0,0); font-size: 1.5em; font-weight: 700; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255,0,0)\"><font face=\"楷体_GB2312\" color=\"#ff80c0\">注意事项：奶瓶在成年人看护下使用。每次使用前应检查瓶体，若有破损 裂痕 等现象 请立即更换。玻璃奶瓶易碎，请避免碰撞 或从高处跌落。通针请置于宝宝接触不到的地方，以免发生意外。</font></span></h2>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'images/201410/thumb_img/395_thumb_G_1413309868654.jpg', 'images/201410/goods_img/395_G_1413309868042.jpg', 'images/201409/source_img/395_G_1410737381232.jpg', '1', '', '1', '1', '0', '0', '1410737381', '100', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '0', '1413244581', '5', '', '-1', '-1', '0', '', '0', '0', '', '', '上海、北京、广东、江苏、浙江、安徽、天津、河北、重庆、湖北、四川、福建、山东单笔订单\"满99包邮\"，全国其他区域单笔订单\"满199包邮\"。 详情请参看<a title=\"配送范围及运费\" style=\"color:#f47050;font-size:14px;\" href=\"article-16.html\">《配送范围及运费》</a>', '0');
