l(http://misc.360buyimg.com/lib/skin/e/i/error-jd.gif); background-position: 50% 50%; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\" /></p>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(255, 85, 127);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: medium;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">材质：</strong><br />\r\n● 聚醚砜PES（Polyether sulfone）<br />\r\n● 聚丙烯PP（Polypropylene）<br />\r\n● 液体硅胶（Liquid Silicone Rubber）</span></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(255, 85, 127);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: medium;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">PES瓶身特点：</strong><br />\r\n● 安心材质：不含可能扰乱内分泌的多种化学物质（环境荷尔蒙：双酚A），广泛使用于医疗器材。<br />\r\n● 高耐热性：耐温可高达180℃，可因应反复高温煮沸、蒸汽消毒、医院的真空高压消毒、微波炉加热消毒及药液消毒。<br />\r\n● 耐药品性：具优良之抗药性及抗酸碱性、可承受一般药水及洗洁剂清洗，不会产生化学变化。<br />\r\n● 耐冲击：强度高，易清洗，不易破裂。<br />\r\n● 奶瓶的蜂蜜颜色是PES的原始天然颜色，绝无添加任何色料。</span></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(255, 85, 127);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: medium;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">奶嘴特点：</strong><br />\r\n● 奶嘴采用食品级硅胶经特殊工艺制成，软硬适中，触感舒适。<br />\r\n● 空气阀设计，奶瓶内外压力能自动保持平衡，奶嘴不易吸扁，让宝宝吸吮流畅，同时可避免因吸入过多空气而引起呕吐或呛奶。<br />\r\n● 十字孔设计，具有不吸不漏及婴儿吸吮力的大小自动调节出奶量的功效。<br />\r\n● 首次使用前用所配通孔针将奶嘴的已剪过的空气阀（正对爱得利商标的那个）和奶嘴头部的十字孔由上往下捅一下，可确保通畅。</span></span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: medium; color: rgb(255, 85, 127);\">耐温：</span></strong></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: medium; color: rgb(255, 85, 127);\">瓶身可耐温至180℃，其他部件可耐温至120℃，可在水中煮沸消毒。</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: medium; color: rgb(255, 85, 127);\">配件：</span></strong></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: medium; color: rgb(255, 85, 127);\">滤网可在喝果汁或奶粉不能充分溶解时使用。防漏片可在短时间携宝宝外出时使用，先配好奶水，将奶嘴倒置放入奶瓶，盖上防漏片，再旋上螺牙，可确保奶水不外溢。</span></span></div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12px;\"><stron