引起的呕吐或呛奶。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 24px;\">十字孔设计，具有不吸不漏及随婴儿吸允力的大小自动调节出奶量的功效。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 24px;\">印刷：所有印刷均采用符合欧洲EN标准的德国产油墨，绝对不含任何重金属成份。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 24px;\">耐温：瓶身可耐温至180℃,其他部件可耐温至120℃,可在水中煮沸消毒.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 24px;\">配件:防尘盖、螺牙、奶嘴、把柄、PES瓶身、自动吸管。</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 24px;\">【使用方法】：</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 1.12em 0px; padding: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(64, 64, 64); font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 24px;\">使用前将各部件清洗干净并放入水中煮沸消毒5分钟(瓶身可耐温至180度，其他部件可耐温至120度）。煮沸消毒时水量应足够，避免产品因长时间接触到温度较高的锅底或锅沿而导致变形。冲调好奶水后，将自动吸管放入奶瓶，套上把柄，再将奶嘴套入螺牙并轻轻往拉出，旋上即可使用。所附塑料棒用于清洗吸管。</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: Arial, Verdana, 宋体; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 18px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); display: inline !important; float: none;\">&nbsp;</span></p>', 'images/201410/thumb_img/412_thumb_G_1413309878935.jpg', 'images/201410/goods_img/412_G_1413309878192.jpg', 'images/201409/source_img/412_G_1410742308493.jpg', '1', '', '1'